snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3702 - 23 Feb 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3702: Gada Pariwaar Ki Nayi Bahu
--------------------------------------------------------
Missa, a friend of Tapu shows up at the Gokuldham society to meet Tapu and give him his diary. Champaklal and Jetha enjoy seeing Tapu interacting warmly with his friend, and Bapuji thinks Missa could end up being their daughter-in-law. Jetha is taken aback by Champaklal's statements, while Sonu exhibits a depressed mood. Missa is brought over by Tapu, who also introduces her to his family. Bapuji is overjoyed to see her because he considers her to be cultured and well-educated. Tapu prevents Sonu from leaving the house while Misha compliments Tapu's coffee and denies having tea made by Sonu. Bhide arrives at his balcony, where he is thrilled to see Missa with Tapu. Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3702, 23 Feb 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.description:
Episode 3703: Bhide Ka Sar Dard
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide was overjoyed to learn of Tapu's girlfriend, and he made "sheera" to inform Madhavi of the news. By telling him the truth that Missa is only a friend and there was a misunderstanding, Sonu breaks his bubble. When Tapu arrives at the society's compound, he decides to play cricket with Tapu Sena in order to remember the memories of his youth. Jetha, Babita, and Dr. Hathi become the audience of the cricket match, Tapu plays a scoop shot on Goli's ball, causing it to strike Bhide on his balcony. Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Live Class 10th English Full Revision Of All Poems | First Flight English Textbook All Poem Revision
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Dear Sir channel's YouTube Live session on "Full Revision of All Poems from Class 10th English Textbook - First Flight". This live session is designed to help students revise all the poems in their English textbook thoroughly.

During this live session, we will cover all the poems included in the Class 10th English textbook, First Flight. The session will provide a comprehensive revision of all the poems, ensuring that students have a clear understanding of the themes, literary devices, and overall structure of each poem.

Some of the poems that will be covered in this live session include "A Tiger in the Zoo", "The Ball Poem", "The Rime of the Ancient Mariner", "Snake", and "Fog". Dear Sir will guide students through each poem, highlighting the key concepts and providing valuable insights to help them improve their understanding and performance in English.

This session is ideal for students preparing for their Class 10th English exams or anyone who wants to deepen their understanding of the poems in the First Flight textbook. Join us for this informative and engaging live session and take the first step towards acing your English exams!

Poems Covered 

Dust of Snow Summary
Fire and Ice Summary
A Tiger in the Zoo Summary
How to Tell Wild Animals Summary
The Ball Poem Summary
Amanda Summary
Animals Summary
The Trees Summary
Fog Summary
The Tale of Custard the Dragon Summary
For Anne Gregory Summary

So, tune in to the Dear Sir channel's YouTube Live session for "Full Revision of All Poems from Class 10th English Textbook - First Flight" and don't miss out on the opportunity to revise all the poems thoroughly.

Don't forget to share with your friends. 

Team Dear Sir

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3703 - Tapu Ne Mara Scoop Shot?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | ‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï ‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

Meta is helping build a future where people have more ways to play and connect in the metaverse. The metaverse may be virtual, but the impact will be real.

Ashish Arora, SK Sir's new student has a habit of constantly jumping from one thing to the next in life and leaves everything incomplete. How will SK Sir deal with his new student?

Tere Bin Episode 19 Teaser - 23rd February 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: 7 Wrong Food Combinations That You Must Avoid
snippet.description:
7 Wrong Food Combinations that you must avoid (With alternative solution). Do not eat these foods together.

Buy WOW Life Science - Peanut Butter with Sattu (Creamy) - https://bit.ly/3PSQSf2
(Apply code FT20 to get 20% off)
Buy from Amazon - https://amzn.to/3m1IDCN

In this video, I share with you 7 Wrong Food combinations that you are eating daily and how you can easily avoid them.

01:07 - #7 Curd and Ghee - Ayurveda states that both ghee and curd are superfoods in themselves but their combination is harmful. Do this instead.
02:04 - #6 Tomato and Cucumber -  If you often consume tomato and cucumber together then Ayurveda advises that you better stop doing so.
02:50 - #5 - Fish and Milk - Does having milk and fish cause white patches? Check it out.
03:35 - #4 Water after Peanuts - Munch on some peanuts and it instantly triggers thirst. Yet, our elders would advise us to never drink water after having peanuts. Why?
04:23 - #3 Milk and Salt - Do you often suffer from skin problems? Checkout for this incompatible food combination in your diet.
05:10 - #2 RIce and Vinegar - Is Chinese fried rice your go-to meal? Or do you like eating sirke wale pyaaz with rice? If yes then be alert.
05:54 - #1 Jaggery and Milk - Are you drinking gud wali chai to avoid the harmful effects of refined sugar? Well, there is more to it.

snippet.description:
Misa, a friend of Tapu's, shows up at the Gokuldham society to meet Tapu and give him his diary. Champaklal and Jetha enjoy seeing Tapu interacting warmly with his friend, and Bapuji thinks Misa could end up being their daughter-in-law. Jetha is taken aback by Champaklal's statements, while Sonu exhibits a depressed mood. Misha is brought over by Tapu, who also introduces her to his family. Bapuji is overjoyed to see her because he considers her to be cultured and well-educated. Tapu prevents Sonu from leaving the house while Misha compliments Tapu's coffee and denies having Sonu's tea. Bhide arrives at his balcony as well, where he is thrilled to see Misha with Tapu. Stay tuned!

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.description:
‡§∂‡•á‡§∞ ‡§¨‡§®‡§ï‡§∞ ‡§∞‡§æ‡§π‡•Å‡§≤ ‡§∞‡•â‡§Ø ‡§®‡•á ‡§ï‡•à‡§∏‡•á ‡§ï‡§ø‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§¶‡•ã‡§∏‡•ç‡§§ ‡§™‡§∞ ‡§π‡§Æ‡§≤‡§æ ? Best Horror Scene Of Junoon Movie starring with Rahul Roy, Pooja Bhatt. 

Vikram is badly injured and his friend is killed by a cursed tiger. He soon learns that the curse has been passed onto him and he will turn into a tiger on a full moon night.

Within the cave, Ravi and Nita are dismayed to discover that there is not one but a row of daggers, only one of which is the right dagger. They read through the manuscript that was given to them by Harry and discover that the setting sun will point towards the right dagger. At sunset, a magical ray enters the cave and enlightens the enchanted dagger. Ravi is overjoyed to see the dagger, but when he claims it, he discovers that Vikram has entered the cave and taken Nita hostage. Vikram offers to exchange Nita with Ravi for the dagger and Ravi agrees to it, but tricks Vikram and a fight ensues. The curse has made Vikram so strong that even in his human form he bests Ravi, but is interrupted before he can finish Ravi when the moon rises. While he is transforming into the tiger, Ravi gets the time to look for the dagger, but is unable to find it due to the mist in the cave. Just before Vikram can finish transforming and kill Ravi, Nita manages to find the dagger and tosses it to Ravi who stabs Vikram with it. This ends the curse as well as killing Vikram, thus bringing to an end the "Junoon" of the curse.

localized.description:
‡§∂‡•á‡§∞ ‡§¨‡§®‡§ï‡§∞ ‡§∞‡§æ‡§π‡•Å‡§≤ ‡§∞‡•â‡§Ø ‡§®‡•á ‡§ï‡•à‡§∏‡•á ‡§ï‡§ø‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§¶‡•ã‡§∏‡•ç‡§§ ‡§™‡§∞ ‡§π‡§Æ‡§≤‡§æ ? Best Horror Scene Of Junoon Movie starring with Rahul Roy, Pooja Bhatt. 

Vikram is badly injured and his friend is killed by a cursed tiger. He soon learns that the curse has been passed onto him and he will turn into a tiger on a full moon night.

Within the cave, Ravi and Nita are dismayed to discover that there is not one but a row of daggers, only one of which is the right dagger. They read through the manuscript that was given to them by Harry and discover that the setting sun will point towards the right dagger. At sunset, a magical ray enters the cave and enlightens the enchanted dagger. Ravi is overjoyed to see the dagger, but when he claims it, he discovers that Vikram has entered the cave and taken Nita hostage. Vikram offers to exchange Nita with Ravi for the dagger and Ravi agrees to it, but tricks Vikram and a fight ensues. The curse has made Vikram so strong that even in his human form he bests Ravi, but is interrupted before he can finish Ravi when the moon rises. While he is transforming into the tiger, Ravi gets the time to look for the dagger, but is unable to find it due to the mist in the cave. Just before Vikram can finish transforming and kill Ravi, Nita manages to find the dagger and tosses it to Ravi who stabs Vikram with it. This ends the curse as well as killing Vikram, thus bringing to an end the "Junoon" of the curse.

#JunoonMovie #RahulRoyMovies #visheshfilms #poojabhatt

As Bihaan and Dhruv try to save Thapki from the goons, Bihaan gets shot by Amma Mai. He holds on for dear life as he asks Thapki to save Bani. Will Bihaan survive the gunshot?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.description:
Raja Rani 2 serial, Riya Vishwanath who played the role of Sandhya IPS in the serial, has given an exclusive interview to IndiaGlitz Tamil to clarify the reason for quitting from Raja Rani 2 serial and the struggle she went through during the shoot, and also about the incidents that happened in the Raja Rani 2 serial and much more...

snippet.description:
"Sachidanand Agnihotri is an honest school teacher. He comes forward to testify against the sexual assault and murder of a young woman. Sachidanand points an accusing finger at Nagesh, the son of a prominent and influential man Jaspal Rana. Due to his statement the police are bound to arrest Nagesh and put him behind the bars. But soon Sachidanand is psychologically tortured and forced to commit suicide. His young son Vishal then takes the law into his own hands in order to avenge his father.

"Sachidanand Agnihotri is an honest school teacher. He comes forward to testify against the sexual assault and murder of a young woman. snippet.description:
With DCP Chitrole now having joined forces with Marco, the whole team CID is left bewildered. As Marco and Chitrole plot to kill the CID inspectors who had gathered in a mall, Sachin and Kavin try to collect some information from witnesses. This eventually leads to Marco being arrested, but a bigger hand is discovered to be in play. Stay tuned to find out!

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
‚Ä¢ Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
‚Ä¢ Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
‚Ä¢ Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
‚Ä¢ Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
‚Ä¢ Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
‚Ä¢ Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
‚Ä¢ Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
‚Ä¢ Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode No: 1114
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #‡§∏‡•Ä‡§Ü‡§à‡§°‡•Ä #sonypal #cid2023 #latestcid #cidfullepisode 

Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sonypali...

About CID: 
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: Quetta Gladiators vs Islamabad United | Highlights | Pakistan Super League | 24th February 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony LIV Channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/sonyliv
 
Click here to watch all highlights: https://bit.ly/3V8TM1y

Click here to watch more: https://www.sonyliv.com/sports/cricket-pakistan-super-league-1700001151

Islamabad United scored a cracking total of 220 runs after their 20 overs. Azam Khan played a brilliant innings worth 97 runs from just 42 balls. Quetta Gladiators lost both their openers quickly and soon the others perished along with them. Quetta Gladiators ended with only 157 runs and were all out by 19.1 overs, giving Islamabad United a 63 run victory.
